{"tid":918233,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"ROG Phone 鬥 Razer Phone 2, 邊隻係 2018 最強電競手機?","createTime":"2018-11-27T04:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T01:57:26.000Z","uid":223235,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8e84c8ffb86cfeb8eb317e35b59f86263c7b07","tid":918233,"uid":223235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"現時市場上的電競手機共有三部 &ndash; Asus ROG Phone、Razer Phone 2 及小米黑鯊Helo, 由於黑鯊Helo並沒有推出港行, 有Magazine 就只針對 Asus ROG Phone 及 Razer Phone 2 作全面比拼!<br />\nMagazine 總結：<br />\nROG Phone 除了配備頂尖的性能之外, 最大的優勢在於從設計、配件至遊戲功能都為電競用家訂身訂造, 回應他們對遊戲設備的訴求。再者筆者認為 ROG Phone 開發團隊的考慮並不單單只局限於電競遊戲, ROG Phone 對育成類遊戲、直向類手遊等等都有作出全方位的照顧, 例如巨集(外掛)設定屬冷門但非常實用的功能! 而在價錢方面，Razer Phone 2 8GB/64G的售價為$6,799，而ROG Phone 8GB/128GB的售價為$7,398。兩者的價錢只相差不過$600。此差價就能換來多64GB的內存，更全面完整的遊戲體驗，再加上實用性高的散熱風扇。在對兩款手機進行深入測試後，筆者認為ROG Phone 為2018 最強電競手機實在當之無慚。<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uEpe13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uEpe13.png&h=d95c158d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網絡圖片"},{"pid":"8d419a9dc21e93ae9fdda5a2f62ebb6b923eaf6a","tid":918233,"uid":12604,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"電莖你個老母 是但拎埋3叔 IPHONE <br />\n都勁撚過/一樣 電莖在哪"},{"pid":"3ee1d2c08142b1029156e97e4c5f603e2c33157c","tid":918233,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"784fd7cd4a6d8abeda8a760de43450a51b4e45af","tid":918233,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119e685361803df2be37ab07bfe20da3e3d37848","tid":918233,"uid":223235,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d419a9dc21e93ae9fdda5a2f62ebb6b923eaf6a","tid":918233,"uid":12604,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"電莖你個老母 是但